Made it safe and sound to California! 🙏🙏 Out here chilling with my west coast brother @quinnsglass for @sawdustartfestival and having a blast checking out all of the people loving their craft out here in Laguna! Here’s a look at a piece I finished up with Quinn before making it out here, our first “Crystal Engraved Flask”!
💎💎💎
This flask features a threaded lid that also doubles as a 10mm joint and comes complete with a 10mm funnel... perfect for iso or other alcohol of your choice... with a very antique feel comfortable this piece has a fully #freehandfaceted cut and polish as well as a “Crystal” engraving... can come with the option of Opal Inlays, be sure to check out the videos above and swipe left for detail shots!
💎💎💎
This piece is now #available, please DM for inquiries if you wanted to make this piece yours! I’ll be out in California for the weekend getting a fresh recharge with the west coast homies, I’ll also have some new #dimensional work available this weekend so be on the lookout thanks all!
🙏🙌⚡️✨
